    "en": {
      "title": "Famous singer passed away",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A.R. Bamba Bhagya made her Tamil debut as a singer in the movie Raavanan with music by Rahman.",
        "Following this, he became famous in a short time by singing many songs in Rahman's music, including 2.O, Bigil, Sarkar, Ponniin Selvan-1.",
        "The song \u201cPonnadhi\u2026\u201d featured in the recently released movie Ponniin Selvan-1 was sung by A.R. He sang along with Rahman. (a)"
      ],
